data.description: Adorable ranch with a new doors, windows, flooring, paint and so much more. Walk up to the cute front porch of the brick home with a red door. Living room with large windows allowing beautiful natural light. Each bedroom has spacious closets.  Huge kitchen overlooking the fully fenced back yard with large Barn Yard Building, at least one blueberry bush, and other beautiful flowering plants. Close to shopping, parks adn beaches! Come see this little gem today!
